## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the impact of outsourcing on employees. The findings are limited to the scope of the articles and reports reviewed, and there may be additional factors influencing the impact of outsourcing that were not covered in the sources consulted. Additionally, the lack of specific publication dates for some sources may affect the timeliness and relevance of the information.